{"tid":2326584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[BigBigShop] 消委會實測午間網上商店送貨，結果係....","createTime":"2020-12-15T11:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:28:34.000Z","uid":123082,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"939fc045775293f4d290bd90cee12d82e9a60ace","tid":2326584,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZGnFrx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZGnFrx.png&h=e5c9ba30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消委會實試五大網上超市，在每間各訂五次貨，五次分別訂購15款不同貨物，包括新鮮、急凍、預先包裝食品和日用品。<br />\n<br />\n消委會發現「HKTVmall」所有訂單，均能按預先選定的送貨時間準時送達。<br />\n<br />\n「百佳」所有訂單亦如期送到，但其中一次有送漏和送錯貨品，要等5和20分鐘再次收貨。<br />\n<br />\n「惠康」的5次實試，有2次送貨遲到，分別遲約2小時和1日。<br />\n<br />\n「city super」其中一次實試，由一次過送貨變成4次分3日送貨，要多2天在家等貨。<br />\n<br />\n「big big shop」5次實試，最終分17張訂單送貨，當中2張突然早到1或5日，8張比原定送貨時間遲到70分鐘至16日，即最遲1張在落單後26日才送到，有3張訂單更是全部貨物都沒送出。<br />\n<br />\nBigbigshop咁既質素都仲有人買就真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416669&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416669%26refer%3DShare&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGCWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9ae68d5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416669%26refer%3DShare&h=af1b0da8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416669&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"79a55502ef278a9f4706db75233f66252c9448f5","tid":2326584,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2618300a90e0b060ec2cdb8f581e640841bad9af","tid":2326584,"uid":166729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"係bigbigshop買野抵撚死"},{"pid":"faf031ce2f65fba046b62d4fdc4d93b86607f1fb","tid":2326584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislik